    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《近巫》作为冒险游戏，包含大量叙事元素，同时带有少许角色扮演的基因，希望既能受到这个游戏类型硬核玩家的欢迎，也能获得新玩家的青睐。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/290ddd083b11401bbc8cad8d8c2aa717.poster.avif?t=1767972779\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/290ddd083b11401bbc8cad8d8c2aa717.webm?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/290ddd083b11401bbc8cad8d8c2aa717.mp4?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就读特兰西瓦尼亚巫法学院，成为近巫，学习法咒的制作方法；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受引人入胜而又有深度的故事，获得冒险游戏的体验；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计自己的法咒组合，每次游戏都有可能产生不同的结果；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几十个吸血鬼、普利克利奇、莫洛伊、斯特里戈伊、食尸鬼、什提马，你的法咒将改变他们的生活；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘美术，4K分辨率，传统动画，逐帧制作；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种服饰和发型供你给主人公设计形象；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特兰西瓦尼亚人开发的游戏，讲述特兰西瓦尼亚的故事！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/4e5822cac591cb11ae4626b1f4e02750.poster.avif?t=1767972779\" width=680 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/4e5822cac591cb11ae4626b1f4e02750.webm?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/4e5822cac591cb11ae4626b1f4e02750.mp4?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你是即将成年的伊利·弗拉扎，应神秘的姨姥姥多姆妮卡邀请来到了特兰西瓦尼亚，结果发现自己上面几代长辈都是女巫，而且得知自己有资格就读特兰西瓦尼亚巫法学院！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/bb26c8603111873ca9cc873efcf00a39.poster.avif?t=1767972779\" width=680 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/bb26c8603111873ca9cc873efcf00a39.webm?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/bb26c8603111873ca9cc873efcf00a39.mp4?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你为了最终能够顺利毕业，成为名副其实的巫师，即将进入暑假预备学校。你将听课学习不同的巫法，看看自己将如何利用日渐强大的能力影响身边生灵的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/fd375e7f2a1e7f24375c5f5f03c5a708.avif?t=1767972779\" width=680 height=284 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为我们自己就是罗马尼亚特兰西瓦尼亚人，所以将深入挖掘本地丰富的民俗传说和迷信观念，依托于这些文化元素打造《近巫》阴暗的多彩世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含三个主要地点，一个是真实存在的锡吉什瓦拉城，一个是特兰西瓦尼亚巫法学院，还有一个是神秘的拉库斯城，坐落于魔法帷幕后面，多数人无法觉察。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在特兰西瓦尼亚巫法学院和周边会遇到各种各样的情况，《近巫》会提供很大的空间，供你自由决定如何应对。你可以随意决定听什么课，也可以翻阅咒书，查找配方，仔细设计你的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/5f83cd73f84f1956a2c22415a563d845.avif?t=1767972779\" width=600 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑的多样性将令部分任务走向不同的结果，影响某些NPC的命运，赋予游戏较高的重玩度。你第一个流程有可能抹掉了某个NPC的记忆，假如这次你对他们用别的法咒呢？或者不用法咒呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《近巫》可以当作指点游戏来玩，也可以直接操控角色，走向目标，全速奔跑，甚至可以飞过去！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/c55819c42aafcc0b4cab8fb65157ffb0.poster.avif?t=1767972779\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/c55819c42aafcc0b4cab8fb65157ffb0.webm?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1685870/extras/c55819c42aafcc0b4cab8fb65157ffb0.mp4?t=1767972779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可以跟同学结仇，也可以交朋友，学习如何掌握自己的巫法天赋，揭晓《近巫》之中古老的秘密！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
